org.kepler.authentication

Class Domain

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.authentication.Domain

  • public class Domain
extends java.lang.Object
    Domain is used to represent the organization which the user belongs to. Users can setup their domain and subdomain, which represent the organization and department/group they belong to, respectively.
    Author:
    Zhijie Guan guan@sdsc.edu
